    "Id": "chassisdef_arbalest_ABT-1",
    "Name": "Arbalest",
    "Details": "The Arbalest 1 is a light 'Mech capable of engaging an enemy at long range, or being used as a light fire support platform. The 'Mech uses its twin Mk.46 Type II LRM-10 launchers to strike an enemy at long range. Should an opponent close, the Arbalest is capable of defending itself at short range with its pair of Series 2a Mk. 5 ER medium lasers. Finally, the head-mounted ECM suite disrupts enemy electronics and proved valuable when disrupting Blakist C3i networks.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Ubiquitous</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.02</color></b>",
